  "commentary": "With SPX at 6775.45 sitting between the max negative gamma at 6770 (-17.7B) and max positive gamma at 6780 (+26.0B), dealers are currently in buying mode as spot trades below the flip at 6788, providing upward pressure toward the 6780 resistance wall. The PIN regime structure suggests dealers will aggressively sell any push above 6780 and buy any dip below 6770, creating a tight 10-point trading range with mean reversion characteristics. The gex_surge event indicates fresh option flow is reinforcing these levels, making 6770 downside support and 6780-6785 the key resistance zone where dealer selling intensifies.\n\nBottom line: expect price to ping-pong between 6770 and 6780 with limited breakout potential.",
